---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="George-AI - Self-hosted AI data platform">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="hero bg-base-200 rounded-lg mb-12">
    <div class="hero-content text-center py-16">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4">George-AI</h1>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8">Centralized vector platform for business users and AI applications</p>
        <p class="mb-8">
          Stop managing separate vector stores for each use case. Collect data from any source like SharePoint, emails, file shares, and databases into one place. Business users search and organize data directly through a modern interface, while n8n workflows, AI agents, and custom applications query the same vector store via API.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-8 font-semibold">
          Data quality for AI - ensure your vectors actually work. Managed by business users. Self-hosted and secure.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="https://github.com/progwise/george-ai" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
            </svg>
            View on GitHub
          </a>
          <a href="/docs" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">
            Read Documentation
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <div class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Key Features</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- Feature 1 -->
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Multi-Source Data Collection & Ingestion</h3>
          <p>Automatic crawlers collect data from SharePoint, Box.com, SMB file shares, and intranet pages. Ingest data from n8n workflows, webhooks, manual uploads, or database connections.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2 -->
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Organize by Business Case, Not Source</h3>
          <p>Group emails, Slack messages, and Office documents together by project or topic—regardless of where they came from. No more hunting across different systems.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3 -->
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Lightning-Fast Search</h3>
          <p>Traditional indexing plus AI-powered Vectors. Find what you need in milliseconds, whether you search by keyword or meaning.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 4 -->
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">No-Code Data Enrichment</h3>
          <p>Business users can enrich and organize data without developer help. Add metadata, tags, and custom fields—all through a simple interface.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 5 -->
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Built for Integration</h3>
          <p>Complete API access for building custom tools. Create AI agents with n8n, embed search components in your intranet, or integrate with existing business applications.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 6 -->
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Smart Data Management</h3>
          <p>Automatic cleanup of outdated data, full audit logging, and access control through Libraries. Vectorization prepares your data for AI agents automatically.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 7 -->
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">AI-Services Clustering & Load Balancing</h3>
          <p>Use all your available Ollama servers with automatic load balancing. Respects GPU speed, memory size, and available models on each server for reliable, high-performance AI processing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <div class="card bg-primary text-primary-content shadow-lg">
    <div class="card-body items-center text-center">
      <h2 class="card-title text-3xl mb-4">Want to see George AI in action?</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Whether you're managing 300,000 supplier documents, searching hospital knowledge bases,
        or tracking projects in email—George AI saves thousands of man-hours every day.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-6 font-semibold">
        Talk to us about your use case and see how George AI can help your organization.
      </p>
      <div class="card-actions">
        <a href="https://calendly.com/michael-vogt-progwise/30min" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">
          Schedule a 30-Minute Demo
        </a>
        <a href="/use-cases" class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg">
          Explore Use Cases
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
